      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers a practical opportunity for a handy buyer, first-time driver, or anyone seeking affordable transportation. It shows wear consistent with age and use, but it remains a solid value with plenty of potential as a daily runabout, backup car, or project. If you're looking for low upfront cost and real utility, this one deserves a look.",
