    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an inexpensive runabout or a great little project? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest budget-friendly option with plenty of life left for the right buyer. A sensible choice for someone who wants affordable wheels without spending a fortune, and a good opportunity if you don\u2019t mind giving it a bit of TLC. Priced to sell and represented straight.",
