    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Honest driver with strong project potential. This car shows its age cosmetically, but the powertrain pulls well, the transmission engages as it should, and it has the kind of solid mechanical feel that makes it a great budget daily, backup vehicle, or weekend fixer-upper. A straightforward platform for someone who wants affordable transportation with room to sort the details over time. Priced to move and worth a look if you want something usable today with upside tomorrow.",
      "price": 6900.0,
