    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character you notice right away\u2014the sort of machine that still has stories left to tell. It\u2019s an affordable way into ownership for someone who appreciates potential, whether you need a budget-friendly runabout, a weekend tinkering project, or a practical set of wheels with plenty of personality. The body and cabin carry the marks of a life well lived, but that\u2019s part of its appeal: no pretension, just straightforward motoring and a chance to make it your own. If you like cars with grit, charm, and room for a fresh chapter, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
